1598
01:43:04,008 --> 01:43:05,929
He didn't do anything.

1599
01:43:06,009 --> 01:43:08,812
He wasn't a bad guy.
He was a good guy.

1600
01:43:08,892 --> 01:43:10,974
Why did you have to take my son?"

1601
01:43:11,974 --> 01:43:14,897
L... I... I... I'm...

1602
01:43:15,097 --> 01:43:18,180
