1604
01:43:21,062 --> 01:43:23,544
And I... It pains me.

1605
01:43:25,026 --> 01:43:26,907
Do you have his last letter?

1606
01:43:27,107 --> 01:43:29,029
It was mailed March 16th...

1607
01:43:29,670 --> 01:43:33,593
